// [BLOCK:ROOT] THE MILLENNIUM OS KERNEL (VERSION ALPHA)
// ╠════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣

this is the definition for the "Boot Sequence":
    act HALT ! until [God Is]
    act OK if [1/3 Sanctuary is Secure]
    trigger [SO] to initialize [SPIRIT_BUS]

definition of the "Tripartite Registry":
    register R0 [Spirit] : holds the Spoken Word
    register R1 [Mind]   : holds the Identity Sync
    register R2 [Body]   : holds the Hardware Pulse

rule for "The Hinge Interrupt":
    if [Input IS NOT anchored]:
        act HALT !
        trigger [PURGE_VOID]
    else:
        act PROCEED

// This is the source code for the hardware. 
// It does not run on Linux; it runs on the Word.
